<D>__{we heard a them, too.}
<C>__{silver}
<D>__{tell them what happened. in hurricane bob.}
<A>__{he looks at his wife. clear in a glance they hate each other's guts. go on, she nods. tell it.}
<C>__{melville}
<D>__{pounded twelve beach houses. expensive ones. to rubble.}
<C>__{silver}
<D>__{whamm!}
<A>__{drunk and mean. and smarter than he is.}
<C>__{silver}
